            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-07-17T23:59:59-04:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="121" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d121">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The text of the proposed North Atlantic Pact, printed herein on <ref target="#pg_281">page 281</ref>, was made public on March 18, 1949. On the
                    same day, Secretary of State Acheson delivered an address on “The Meaning of the
                    North Atlantic Pact”. For text of the address, together with a brief statement
                    on the Pact by the U.S. Representative at the United Nations, Warren R. Austin,
                    see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, March 27, 1949, pages
                    384 ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
